221
00:10:36,667 --> 00:10:37,667
Ooh…

222
00:10:37,834 --> 00:10:38,834
Really?

223
00:10:39,554 --> 00:10:40,887
I have to try it.

224
00:10:48,865 --> 00:10:50,419
Well? What else
are you waiting for?

225
00:10:50,832 --> 00:10:51,832
I’m just kidding!

226
00:10:52,630 --> 00:10:53,630
I was just kidding…

227
00:10:53,945 --> 00:10:57,125
Didn’t you say you want this?
Just like this?

228
00:10:58,023 --> 00:10:59,249
I wanted this?!

229
00:10:59,849 --> 00:11:02,103
Orb, you’re an embarrassment.

230
00:11:02,282 --> 00:11:04,602
How did you get involved
with those peeping toms?!

231
00:11:04,969 --> 00:11:07,029
It’s Iskineport’s fault!

232
00:11:07,945 --> 00:11:10,005
I promise,
I was just dragged into this!

233
00:11:10,139 --> 00:11:11,146
Yeah,

234
00:11:11,292 --> 00:11:13,858
but you now have a
record in our barangay.

235
00:11:16,133 --> 00:11:17,133
You know what,

236
00:11:17,726 --> 00:11:21,759
I’m doubtful about the sudden
sprouting of that Alice.

237
00:11:22,100 --> 00:11:23,100
That’s what I’m saying.

238
00:11:23,153 --> 00:11:26,199
And now, your Tso K is
getting dragged into it, too!

239
00:11:30,325 --> 00:11:31,325
Okay, so what,

240
00:11:32,576 --> 00:11:34,996
you’re becoming
busybodies now, too?!

241
00:11:35,705 --> 00:11:37,231
Tso K, you’ve known it since,

242
00:11:37,357 --> 00:11:39,132
every time we get
a problem here,

243
00:11:39,157 --> 00:11:40,731
your name always gets
dragged into whatever it is.

244
00:11:40,858 --> 00:11:41,871
What do you mean?

245
00:11:41,896 --> 00:11:44,211
That you’re always getting
seen in the barangay.

246
00:11:44,286 --> 00:11:46,706
Hmmm? What do you
think of me, a lug along?

247
00:11:47,652 --> 00:11:49,338
All Anne is saying is

248
00:11:49,718 --> 00:11:51,538
that your good name
is getting tainted.

249
00:11:52,045 --> 00:11:53,598
My name is getting tainted?

250
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,613
Exactly, Tso K.

251
00:11:57,573 --> 00:11:58,573
Well then,

252
00:11:58,660 --> 00:12:02,587
let me prove to you that
the name Chef K is clean.

253
00:12:05,997 --> 00:12:07,503
How?

254
00:12:08,723 --> 00:12:09,723
All together now?

255
00:12:12,442 --> 00:12:13,908
Barangay hearing?!

256
00:12:13,995 --> 00:12:15,162
Barangay hearing?!

257
00:12:15,640 --> 00:12:16,920
Barangay hearing?!

258
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,147
Barangay hearing?!

259
00:12:18,307 --> 00:12:20,067
BARANGAY HEARING?!

260
00:12:20,298 --> 00:12:21,298
Yeah!

261
00:12:21,998 --> 00:12:24,227
I personally approached
our barangay captain

262
00:12:24,252 --> 00:12:26,451
for us to do a barangay hearing!

263
00:12:26,952 --> 00:12:29,052
Why do we need to
have a barangay hearing?

264
00:12:29,445 --> 00:12:31,393
I need a barangay hearing

265
00:12:31,417 --> 00:12:35,725
because I need to clean and
clear my name! Chef K!

266
00:12:36,241 --> 00:12:38,108
Well then, if you’re just
going to clear your name,

267
00:12:38,248 --> 00:12:40,141
why don’t you just
run it under hot water,

268
00:12:40,208 --> 00:12:43,744
soap it up and scrape off the dirt!
Wash it like it’s laundry!

269
00:12:43,871 --> 00:12:46,511
That’s such a shame,
you’re so brainless!

270
00:12:47,304 --> 00:12:49,477
But Chef K, that’s a good idea

271
00:12:49,518 --> 00:12:53,311
so the rumors swirling between
you and Alice would stop!

272
00:12:53,379 --> 00:12:54,866
You know what, you’re right.

273
00:12:54,932 --> 00:12:58,898
I’ve been here for so long
but I don’t know any Alice.

274
00:12:59,259 --> 00:13:01,944
- That’s right-
- Where did you study at, sweetie?

275
00:13:02,084 --> 00:13:03,238
Actually,

276
00:13:04,356 --> 00:13:07,349
every time I get asked
where I studied,

277
00:13:08,059 --> 00:13:09,879
I’m embarrassed to say

278
00:13:10,139 --> 00:13:11,832
but I underwent tutorial.

279
00:13:12,084 --> 00:13:13,971
I was homeschooled on our farm.

280
00:13:16,173 --> 00:13:17,759
Okay, Alice,
that’s enough.

281
00:13:18,079 --> 00:13:19,266
No more statements!

282
00:13:19,864 --> 00:13:22,151
Let’s just talk about this
in the Barangay, alright?!

283
00:13:23,071 --> 00:13:35,393
Hearing! Hearing! Hearing!
Hearing! Hearing! Hearing!

284
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:36,787
Salamat, Luningning!
Thank you, Luningning!

285
00:13:36,833 --> 00:13:38,754
- Oh, thank you, too!
- Thank you!

286
00:13:42,377 --> 00:13:43,458
- Uncle,
- Hmm?

287
00:13:46,202 --> 00:13:49,369
Why don’t we just admit that
we do run the POGO business

288
00:13:49,481 --> 00:13:50,734
so we can just skip the hearing?

289
00:13:50,827 --> 00:13:52,207
Are you crazy?!

290
00:13:52,627 --> 00:13:55,487
If you do that,
they’ll take over the POGO!

291
00:13:56,761 --> 00:13:59,688
But I don’t want for the people
to think badly about us.

292
00:13:59,848 --> 00:14:01,061
Oh, let them.

293
00:14:01,340 --> 00:14:03,080
You know,
no matter what you say,

294
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:07,826
people will believe
what they wanna believe.

295
00:14:08,427 --> 00:14:09,546
So, just let them be.

296
00:14:09,993 --> 00:14:13,320
Right, I get that, Uncle.
I understand.

297
00:14:14,852 --> 00:14:16,439
- Take a video of it!
- Video? Take a video?

298
00:14:16,466 --> 00:14:17,906
Yes, a video!
Can you see it well?

299
00:14:18,266 --> 00:14:20,938
But there are leaves,
can’t you see?!

300
00:14:21,792 --> 00:14:24,232
Then push them out of the way!

301
00:14:25,212 --> 00:14:26,212
Geez.

302
00:14:28,021 --> 00:14:32,307
Gosh, a lot of people are going
to enjoy our POGO business.

303
00:14:32,558 --> 00:14:33,745
Oh, that’s for sure!

304
00:14:33,847 --> 00:14:37,684
The players will keep on
coming back for more of POGO!

305
00:14:38,764 --> 00:14:39,764
Of course –

306
00:14:43,546 --> 00:14:46,726
Hey! Are you taking
a video of us?! Huh?!

307
00:14:46,925 --> 00:14:48,251
Aaahhh…

308
00:14:48,731 --> 00:14:52,891
No, we’re taking a video of the games
because we have a documentary film.

309
00:14:52,971 --> 00:14:56,611
We need to know if these are
living things are non living things.

310
00:14:56,638 --> 00:14:57,871
Or if they can be eaten or not.

311
00:14:59,810 --> 00:15:01,000
Are you sure?!

312
00:15:01,025 --> 00:15:02,268
- Yes.
- Non-living things.

313
00:15:03,203 --> 00:15:05,463
Oh, alright. I thought you were
taking a video of us, that’s not allowed!

314
00:15:05,488 --> 00:15:06,488
Yeah!

315
00:15:06,637 --> 00:15:07,637
Let’s see!

316
00:15:09,344 --> 00:15:10,464
- Chard, wait up!
- Yeah.

317
00:15:10,531 --> 00:15:11,897
- This is your phone, isn’t it?
- Yeah.

318
00:15:11,971 --> 00:15:13,497
Where’s the video that you took?

319
00:15:13,886 --> 00:15:14,886
What?

320
00:15:14,911 --> 00:15:18,426
Show kuya Aga
the video you took!

321
00:15:19,330 --> 00:15:20,617
The video record?

322
00:15:22,130 --> 00:15:23,497
Mm-mm. Show it to them, come on.

323
00:15:23,744 --> 00:15:25,670
Hey why are you on my lap?!

324
00:15:26,484 --> 00:15:27,484
I can’t remember!

325
00:15:27,509 --> 00:15:31,312
Show the video you took,
the record between Chef K and Alice!

326
00:15:31,345 --> 00:15:32,658
Didn’t I ask you to record it?!

327
00:15:32,740 --> 00:15:35,320
Iskineport said you had a video!

328
00:15:35,353 --> 00:15:36,353
I do, Ate Cha.

329
00:15:36,948 --> 00:15:38,208
Video record?

330
00:15:39,432 --> 00:15:41,938
I told you to take
a video, didn’t I?

331
00:15:42,870 --> 00:15:44,428
Oh,

332
00:15:44,452 --> 00:15:47,210
- the one with the two talking?
- Yeah!

333
00:15:47,235 --> 00:15:49,882
- Chef K and-
- Yeah, you told me to record it and…

334
00:15:49,907 --> 00:15:51,340
- Exactly!
- The one where we were quiet?

335
00:15:51,365 --> 00:15:53,331
- Right, that one!
- The one where I almost coughed?!

336
00:15:53,356 --> 00:15:55,126
Yes, that’s exactly it!

337
00:15:55,867 --> 00:15:56,867
Oh, my battery was empty then.

338
00:15:57,012 --> 00:15:58,578
- So you weren’t able to record it?
- No, I wasn’t.

339
00:16:00,742 --> 00:16:01,742
Ow!

340
00:16:02,714 --> 00:16:07,133
Wait, wait, wait! That’s okay,
that’s okay. Wait, wait! It’s all okay!

341
00:16:09,819 --> 00:16:16,167
If you don’t have a video record
against Chef K, well then, I do!

342
00:16:16,345 --> 00:16:17,345
What?!

343
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:19,140
You were able to secure
evidence against Chef K?!

344
00:16:19,805 --> 00:16:23,504
My love, don’t you remember, he and I
have known each other for a long time!

345
00:16:24,790 --> 00:16:26,050
You’re so great!

346
00:16:26,141 --> 00:16:27,441
There’s the evidence!

347
00:16:28,045 --> 00:16:29,492
We can use that against them!

348
00:16:30,773 --> 00:16:31,900
That’s right!

349
00:16:32,826 --> 00:16:33,826
What?!

350
00:16:33,896 --> 00:16:36,176
Chef K is going to get dragged into it!

351
00:16:36,271 --> 00:16:39,197
Well it’s because you accused him
of doing something illegal first!

352
00:16:40,826 --> 00:16:43,626
Uh, actually, Boss Beauty,

353
00:16:44,078 --> 00:16:49,292
Captain is right, you did say that
Chef K was doing something illegal.

354
00:16:49,697 --> 00:16:50,903
You said it!

355
00:16:51,652 --> 00:16:52,652
Would you look at this?!

356
00:16:52,771 --> 00:16:54,597
Weren’t you the one being nosy!

357
00:16:54,730 --> 00:16:56,790
You were the one
who told me about it!

358
00:16:58,158 --> 00:16:59,485
Oh my gosh, really?

359
00:16:59,510 --> 00:17:01,111
I can’t remember.

360
00:17:01,136 --> 00:17:05,149
Everything that you’re accusing Chef K of,
prove that in the hearing tomorrow!

361
00:17:05,174 --> 00:17:06,243
He might sue you, you know!

362
00:17:06,287 --> 00:17:07,780
I can take a summon!

363
00:17:08,160 --> 00:17:10,113
Excuse me, what?! A summon?!

364
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:11,940
Why us, though?!

365
00:17:11,965 --> 00:17:13,438
Why is he going to summon us?!

366
00:17:13,463 --> 00:17:16,045
Don’t sneak in on me, you might
cause me to stand up all of a sudden!

367
00:17:16,070 --> 00:17:17,070
Oh my go–

368
00:17:17,095 --> 00:17:18,819
Boss Beauty, breathe, breathe!

369
00:17:18,844 --> 00:17:22,405
Yes, Boss Beauty, breathe!

370
00:17:22,591 --> 00:17:26,507
Support your evidence.
Support your evidence, you hear me?

371
00:17:26,719 --> 00:17:30,222
For all your accusations against Alice,
most especially against Chef K!

372
00:17:30,247 --> 00:17:33,126
- Can’t breathe!
- Breathe in!

373
00:17:34,676 --> 00:17:36,096
Correct, correct form! You can do it!

374
00:17:39,715 --> 00:17:40,715
Quiet, quiet!

375
00:17:41,407 --> 00:17:43,361
Let’s begin our hearing.

376
00:17:44,066 --> 00:17:49,099
Barangay Singko vs. Alice Po-Go and Chef K!

377
00:17:49,154 --> 00:17:51,824
The issue: Illegal POGO business!

378
00:17:52,251 --> 00:17:55,897
Iskineport will be the
advocate for the accused.

379
00:17:56,870 --> 00:17:58,390
Thank you, your first honor.

380
00:18:04,183 --> 00:18:05,183
What?

381
00:18:06,305 --> 00:18:07,558
He looks like a gay electrician.

382
00:18:08,189 --> 00:18:10,195
Chef K, I’m an attorney here.

383
00:18:11,206 --> 00:18:15,802
May I call on Mariposa on
the witness stand, please?

384
00:18:15,830 --> 00:18:17,834
Oh, hey, that’s me!

385
00:18:20,013 --> 00:18:22,013
Thank you fans, thank you fans!

386
00:18:22,038 --> 00:18:23,038
Quiet.

387
00:18:24,368 --> 00:18:25,462
Hand on the bible.

388
00:18:26,403 --> 00:18:27,403
Okay.

389
00:18:27,610 --> 00:18:28,897
I swear to tell…

390
00:18:29,653 --> 00:18:31,547
to tell but nothing but the truth…

391
00:18:32,206 --> 00:18:34,013
the truth, but nothing but to tell…

392
00:18:34,279 --> 00:18:35,519
the truth will set you free.

393
00:18:36,709 --> 00:18:37,996
Yeah, I swear!

394
00:18:38,802 --> 00:18:39,802
Thank you!

395
00:18:44,738 --> 00:18:46,385
My question for you is-

396
00:18:47,691 --> 00:18:49,377
what is your hip measurement?

397
00:18:50,025 --> 00:18:51,065
Objection, your honor!

398
00:18:51,345 --> 00:18:52,951
What does the size of my hip
have to do with any of this?!

399
00:18:53,617 --> 00:18:54,617
No, your honor!

400
00:18:54,875 --> 00:18:57,681
I need to know her hip measurement!

401
00:18:59,629 --> 00:19:02,789
Chef K, Chef K, Chef K!

402
00:19:04,154 --> 00:19:06,374
You’ve never learned.

403
00:19:08,271 --> 00:19:15,507
Len-len! Len-len! Len-len!
Len-len! Len-len! Len-len!

404
00:19:18,143 --> 00:19:20,923
Chef K, you seem like
you want to wreck our family!

405
00:19:21,525 --> 00:19:23,605
Just like Danica Paras’ family!

406
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:32,109
The reason why I’m asking
for her hip measurement

407
00:19:32,133 --> 00:19:34,541
is because I want to establish

408
00:19:34,952 --> 00:19:39,486
if Mariposa is

409
00:19:42,776 --> 00:19:44,363
in the right state of mind.

410
00:19:46,457 --> 00:19:47,457
Well,

411
00:19:47,724 --> 00:19:50,637
thank you for that
wonderful question!

412
00:19:51,103 --> 00:19:54,624
I don’t feel any fressure right now!

413
00:19:55,706 --> 00:20:01,495
My vital statistics is 36-23-36!

414
00:20:01,520 --> 00:20:02,520
Wow!

415
00:20:03,808 --> 00:20:05,941
Are you satisfied with my answer?

416
00:20:06,245 --> 00:20:07,245
Yes, Mariposa.

417
00:20:07,547 --> 00:20:08,652
Actually, your answer
was more than enough.

418
00:20:08,677 --> 00:20:10,169
I was just asking for
your hip measurement,

419
00:20:10,194 --> 00:20:12,179
and yet you gave me
your full vital statistics!

420
00:20:12,840 --> 00:20:15,014
You must take your seat,
or I will be dead.

421
00:20:15,497 --> 00:20:17,877
Thank you!

422
00:20:22,062 --> 00:20:23,749
Excuse me, your honor.

423
00:20:23,895 --> 00:20:26,086
- Yes?
- Not you. Him.

424
00:20:26,111 --> 00:20:28,009
- Continue your questioning, Aga.
- Thank you.

425
00:20:28,034 --> 00:20:32,069
Uh, your honor,
may I continue my questioning?

426
00:20:32,328 --> 00:20:33,328
Proceed.

427
00:20:33,404 --> 00:20:34,632
Wait a second.
Excuse me.

428
00:20:34,817 --> 00:20:35,817
My love, hold on a moment.

429
00:20:37,038 --> 00:20:39,378
You sound like you’re
asking the wrong questions.

430
00:20:39,503 --> 00:20:43,257
Don’t you dare make a mistake,
Ate Charlene is watching.

431
00:20:43,616 --> 00:20:44,956
- Okay?
- I was just gonna ask questions.

432
00:20:45,068 --> 00:20:50,618
So your vision is impaired
and you won’t sin, come closer to Mariposa.

433
00:20:53,517 --> 00:20:54,517
Mariposa…

434
00:20:55,284 --> 00:20:56,284
oh here.

435
00:20:56,399 --> 00:20:58,585
- I’m here!
- They took my glasses!

436
00:20:58,985 --> 00:20:59,985
Stop it!

437
00:21:01,102 --> 00:21:03,087
My love, I’m gonna go ahead
and ask questions.

438
00:21:03,112 --> 00:21:07,778
Uh, this is complicated.

439
00:21:08,637 --> 00:21:11,909
It’s hard to even form a question.
But, my question is–do you pray?

440
00:21:13,370 --> 00:21:14,883
At night, yes.

441
00:21:15,030 --> 00:21:16,030
Good.

442
00:21:16,492 --> 00:21:20,739
When you respond to the elderly,
do you say your “po” and “opo”?

443
00:21:21,430 --> 00:21:22,430
Yes, I do.

444
00:21:23,553 --> 00:21:24,906
- That’s it, your honor.
- Thank you very much.

445
00:21:25,075 --> 00:21:26,075
Thank you.

446
00:21:26,650 --> 00:21:27,650
Well that was rather kind.

447
00:21:30,275 --> 00:21:33,110
You know what, you’re gonna go straight
to Pluto and go beyond heaven.

448
00:21:33,865 --> 00:21:34,865
You’re too nice!

449
00:21:35,132 --> 00:21:36,918
Yes! Thank you, your honor!

450
00:21:39,348 --> 00:21:41,122
Where are Atasha and Andres?

451
00:21:42,025 --> 00:21:44,065
The hearing recess is about to be over!

452
00:21:44,249 --> 00:21:48,502
Maybe they’re having a hard time
looking for evidence against Chef K?

453
00:21:48,726 --> 00:21:49,992
- Cha, Aga!
- Lola Maxi!

454
00:21:50,279 --> 00:21:51,799
Aren’t they here yet?

455
00:21:52,060 --> 00:21:55,446
There’s only five minutes left,
we need to go back to the barangay hearing!

456
00:21:55,471 --> 00:21:57,537
That’s what I’m saying!

457
00:21:57,858 --> 00:21:59,449
- Oh, here! Here!
- Here they come!

458
00:21:59,474 --> 00:22:01,395
Chef K’s old [inaudible]!

459
00:22:01,420 --> 00:22:02,420
Okay?

460
00:22:02,424 --> 00:22:04,470
Maybe we can use this on the hearing!

461
00:22:04,509 --> 00:22:05,983
That’s what I’ve been saying!

462
00:22:07,136 --> 00:22:08,878
- Here, here.
- Ooh, Chef K will be caught off guard

463
00:22:08,903 --> 00:22:11,735
because we have evidence against him.

464
00:22:12,359 --> 00:22:13,359
Mm-mm!

465
00:22:13,892 --> 00:22:15,538
The hearing is about to-

466
00:22:17,060 --> 00:22:18,287
Isn’t that a photo album?

467
00:22:18,362 --> 00:22:19,995
Oh, this?

468
00:22:20,654 --> 00:22:22,933
- Yeah!
- No, don’t mind this. Don’t.

469
00:22:28,136 --> 00:22:29,136
It was you?

470
00:22:31,169 --> 00:22:35,620
You helped them
find evidence against me?

471
00:22:36,098 --> 00:22:37,472
You, my own flesh and blood?

472
00:22:38,787 --> 00:22:40,373
- Tso K…
- Don’t Tso K me!

473
00:22:40,957 --> 00:22:42,390
And you! My BFF!

474
00:22:42,774 --> 00:22:44,187
BFF!

475
00:22:44,762 --> 00:22:47,336
I never thought
you’d do this to me!

476
00:22:47,940 --> 00:22:48,940
No, it’s okay.

477
00:22:49,408 --> 00:22:50,408
It’s all good and fine!

478
00:22:50,539 --> 00:22:51,539
Proceed with it!

479
00:22:51,799 --> 00:22:52,799
Okay?!

480
00:22:53,246 --> 00:22:54,246
Good luck!

481
00:22:55,088 --> 00:22:56,408
May the best man win!

482
00:23:08,956 --> 00:23:11,323
Okay, hearing will now resume.

483
00:23:12,169 --> 00:23:15,320
Chef K, please present your witness.

484
00:23:17,988 --> 00:23:19,668
The judge’s voice is too soft!

485
00:23:21,298 --> 00:23:24,914
May I call on Ross Beauty?

486
00:23:25,526 --> 00:23:26,526
Boss Beauty!

487
00:23:27,156 --> 00:23:28,808
Did you just say Ross?
Where did Ross come from?

488
00:23:28,833 --> 00:23:29,847
Who is Ross?

489
00:23:30,638 --> 00:23:31,878
Is there a Ross here?

490
00:23:32,563 --> 00:23:34,447
- No one. No!
- Rose. Rose!

491
00:23:34,527 --> 00:23:36,034
- Boss, boss.
- That’s you.

492
00:23:36,064 --> 00:23:37,318
- Boss Beauty.
- This is Rose.

493
00:23:38,262 --> 00:23:39,329
That's new-

494
00:23:40,364 --> 00:23:41,477
I swear to tell…

495
00:23:42,496 --> 00:23:44,163
to tell but nothing but the truth…

496
00:23:44,545 --> 00:23:45,625
the truth will set you free.

497
00:23:45,971 --> 00:23:46,971
I swear.

498
00:23:52,360 --> 00:23:53,360
Boss Beauty,

499
00:23:54,497 --> 00:23:57,570
do you think Mariposa
is telling the truth

500
00:23:58,093 --> 00:24:01,667
about me running an illegal business–

501
00:24:01,953 --> 00:24:05,507
POGO business–with Alicia Poe-Go?

502
00:24:06,912 --> 00:24:07,912
Yes!

503
00:24:08,558 --> 00:24:09,558
That’s right!

504
00:24:10,390 --> 00:24:12,630
Mariposa is lying!

505
00:24:15,075 --> 00:24:16,389
Are you calling me a liar?!

506
00:24:16,675 --> 00:24:18,022
That’s all for now, your honor.

507
00:24:18,047 --> 00:24:19,047
Okay.

508
00:24:27,095 --> 00:24:28,288
- First honor,
- Yes?

509
00:24:28,365 --> 00:24:31,098
…may I ask questions and
run my cross examination?

510
00:24:31,238 --> 00:24:32,238
Yes, please proceed.

511
00:24:32,361 --> 00:24:36,887
May I call on Alice Poe-Go
in the witness stand?

512
00:24:41,607 --> 00:24:43,114
Here we go, Kap!

513
00:24:46,657 --> 00:24:47,657
You’re a spy!

514
00:24:50,183 --> 00:24:51,183
I know it!

515
00:24:54,626 --> 00:24:59,444
Answer my question truthfully,
just like they said–you’re a spy!

516
00:24:59,737 --> 00:25:00,851
Can you explain?

517
00:25:04,187 --> 00:25:06,461
I’m not a spy.

518
00:25:07,037 --> 00:25:09,443
I’m a Filipino.

519
00:25:10,076 --> 00:25:12,869
I love my neighbors!

520
00:25:16,278 --> 00:25:17,905
You love your neighbors?

521
00:25:19,719 --> 00:25:22,093
If you say you love your neighbors,

522
00:25:23,459 --> 00:25:25,545
then what time do you shower?

523
00:25:26,251 --> 00:25:28,118
Where and what time
do you wash up?

524
00:25:28,143 --> 00:25:29,171
Do you do that in your bathroom?

525
00:25:29,483 --> 00:25:32,770
Or do you do that
in other people’s bathrooms?

526
00:25:36,861 --> 00:25:37,861
Your honor,

527
00:25:38,352 --> 00:25:39,799
as much as possible,

528
00:25:40,387 --> 00:25:43,074
I don’t want to talk
about my private life!

529
00:25:43,253 --> 00:25:44,253
Answer the question!

530
00:25:44,353 --> 00:25:45,739
Don’t lie!

531
00:25:45,919 --> 00:25:48,280
I’ve been asking you questions now
and your answers are non-sense!

532
00:25:48,594 --> 00:25:49,594
Ow!

533
00:25:51,930 --> 00:25:52,930
Your honor,

534
00:25:53,088 --> 00:25:54,861
I apologize; to everyone,

535
00:25:55,034 --> 00:25:58,933
Iskineport just got carried away,
and he’s gotten upset,

536
00:25:59,532 --> 00:26:04,113
and now we can also
feel how upset his is.

537
00:26:04,893 --> 00:26:08,832
Now, Alice, please return.

538
00:26:09,494 --> 00:26:10,594
Thank you.

539
00:26:10,685 --> 00:26:11,685
- Thank you!
- Careful.

540
00:26:11,710 --> 00:26:12,803
Thank you. Thank you, Alice.

541
00:26:14,126 --> 00:26:15,126
Your honor,

542
00:26:15,745 --> 00:26:18,832
may I call on Chef K
on the witness stand?

543
00:26:20,588 --> 00:26:21,848
Chef K, please.

544
00:26:30,828 --> 00:26:32,194
Oh, someone’s adlibbing.

545
00:26:32,628 --> 00:26:33,628
Chef K…

546
00:26:33,940 --> 00:26:36,273
Do you really think you
can sully my name, BFF?

547
00:26:36,980 --> 00:26:37,980
Let’s see.

548
00:26:38,213 --> 00:26:39,213
Sit down, please.

549
00:26:39,499 --> 00:26:40,499
Try me.

550
00:26:41,713 --> 00:26:43,114
Ah, Chef K,

551
00:26:44,035 --> 00:26:47,698
we’ve gathered
some photos and videos here.

552
00:26:48,805 --> 00:26:49,805
Now,

553
00:26:50,066 --> 00:26:54,708
can you please explain to this
court what these photos are?

554
00:26:55,272 --> 00:26:56,818
Please, Chef K?

555
00:26:57,262 --> 00:26:58,936
Wait, what does this mean?

556
00:26:58,961 --> 00:26:59,961
What is this?

557
00:27:00,155 --> 00:27:01,268
Why do I look like a rat here?

558
00:27:01,748 --> 00:27:02,748
Here!

559
00:27:03,218 --> 00:27:04,345
Look here and well!

560
00:27:05,064 --> 00:27:06,211
- Where did you get this?
- There it is!

561
00:27:07,163 --> 00:27:08,737
Chef K, take a good look at those.

562
00:27:10,802 --> 00:27:11,802
Hey…

563
00:27:12,242 --> 00:27:13,242
Is that me?

564
00:27:14,668 --> 00:27:15,668
Hey!

565
00:27:16,308 --> 00:27:17,308
You see it here–

566
00:27:17,838 --> 00:27:20,225
sepia, black, and white…

567
00:27:20,859 --> 00:27:22,133
You’re really mad at me,
aren’t you?

568
00:27:22,275 --> 00:27:23,361
You still have a mustache here…

569
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:24,869
What the hell, what –

570
00:27:24,894 --> 00:27:26,356
Chef K! Thank you very much!

571
00:27:27,166 --> 00:27:28,613
Wait what were you saying!

572
00:27:28,638 --> 00:27:30,231
It’s not good, it’s not good!

573
00:27:30,496 --> 00:27:31,583
I’m not… black and white!

574
00:27:32,063 --> 00:27:33,323
Why is there a black
and white, though?

575
00:27:33,348 --> 00:27:36,497
Because you were born in the 50s.

576
00:27:36,715 --> 00:27:38,195
Oh, hey…that’s too much.

577
00:27:38,861 --> 00:27:40,201
People might believe you!

578
00:27:40,226 --> 00:27:42,400
So, please, explain to us…
is that true or not?

579
00:27:42,507 --> 00:27:44,180
- It’s not!
- Okay! Your honor…

580
00:27:44,517 --> 00:27:46,263
this just means one thing–

581
00:27:46,876 --> 00:27:49,016
that Chef K really has a kind heart.

582
00:27:49,938 --> 00:27:52,818
From since then until now,
you’ve seen him.

583
00:27:52,884 --> 00:27:54,030
He’s a good man.

584
00:27:54,450 --> 00:27:59,770
And as proof that
his POGO business is legal.

585
00:28:00,396 --> 00:28:02,303
Let’s pull out all the evidence!

586
00:28:02,594 --> 00:28:04,107
Iskineport, Andres,

587
00:28:05,527 --> 00:28:06,527
please!

588
00:28:07,644 --> 00:28:08,644
That’s it!

589
00:28:09,638 --> 00:28:12,798
That’s the business!

590
00:28:14,078 --> 00:28:16,392
Quail egg?!

591
00:28:16,873 --> 00:28:17,920
Quail eggs?!

592
00:28:18,429 --> 00:28:19,769
Awesome, yeah?

593
00:28:20,006 --> 00:28:21,340
BFF!

594
00:28:21,453 --> 00:28:22,453
Yes?

595
00:28:23,026 --> 00:28:24,026
BFF..

596
00:28:25,580 --> 00:28:26,580
Thank you!

597
00:28:27,216 --> 00:28:28,216
That is true!

598
00:28:28,631 --> 00:28:30,571
Berting Labra is not at fault!

599
00:28:36,424 --> 00:28:37,424
What?

600
00:28:41,405 --> 00:28:42,405
Wait!

601
00:28:42,931 --> 00:28:44,124
Why did you put this out?!

602
00:28:44,498 --> 00:28:46,405
Why did you reveal my business?!

603
00:28:46,430 --> 00:28:48,770
Now everyone will be
out to compete with me,

604
00:28:48,843 --> 00:28:52,712
and now Alicia Poe-Go’s
business will deplete!

605
00:28:56,211 --> 00:28:57,351
That’s it, your honor.

606
00:28:58,004 --> 00:28:59,031
Everything is cleared!

607
00:28:59,259 --> 00:29:00,259
Except for you.

608
00:29:01,336 --> 00:29:02,563
That’s why I’m saying it.

609
00:29:02,753 --> 00:29:04,407
Your quail egg business is approved.

610
00:29:04,693 --> 00:29:06,427
So, it is clear, Chef K is innocent.

611
00:29:06,895 --> 00:29:07,895
Okay?

612
00:29:08,155 --> 00:29:10,349
This case is dismissed…
barangay hearing is now adjourned.

613
00:29:10,376 --> 00:29:11,582
- What?!
- What did you just say?!

614
00:29:12,460 --> 00:29:13,853
You’re messing everything up!

615
00:29:14,304 --> 00:29:16,510
Chef K, no!
That’s our barangay captain!

616
00:29:17,636 --> 00:29:18,716
My neighbors,

617
00:29:19,271 --> 00:29:22,985
I just want to take everyone
of you because I just realized

618
00:29:23,326 --> 00:29:26,018
that doing an underground
business is not right.

619
00:29:27,442 --> 00:29:28,656
- No, but–Yes?
- Uncle,

620
00:29:28,929 --> 00:29:30,642
I also want to say sorry to you.

621
00:29:31,363 --> 00:29:33,316
Your name was almost sullied…

622
00:29:34,225 --> 00:29:36,731
Not really.
If you think about it,

623
00:29:37,046 --> 00:29:39,799
we didn’t spread fake news.

624
00:29:39,824 --> 00:29:42,730
Oh but of course,
we shouldn’t be affected by anything

625
00:29:43,090 --> 00:29:46,297
since we didn’t do anything wrong.

626
00:29:46,656 --> 00:29:48,550
Our conscience is clear.

627
00:29:49,318 --> 00:29:50,318
Tso K,

628
00:29:50,417 --> 00:29:51,921
if your business is legal,

629
00:29:51,945 --> 00:29:53,631
why did you feel the need
to hide it from everyone!

630
00:29:54,036 --> 00:29:55,249
Oh…

631
00:29:55,363 --> 00:29:57,223
First of all,

632
00:29:58,173 --> 00:29:59,213
it’s not “Tso K,”

633
00:30:00,408 --> 00:30:01,508
it’s “Chef K!”

634
00:30:02,421 --> 00:30:03,421
Secondly,

635
00:30:04,020 --> 00:30:05,767
why do I need to
explain myself to you?

636
00:30:07,039 --> 00:30:08,405
- Oh!
- And why

637
00:30:08,430 --> 00:30:11,627
do we need to spread the news
about our business to everyone?

638
00:30:11,665 --> 00:30:12,665
Tell me why!

639
00:30:12,692 --> 00:30:13,692
That’s right!

640
00:30:13,717 --> 00:30:16,307
Because sometimes,
the people who really don’t have anything

641
00:30:16,337 --> 00:30:18,946
to do with the whole story,
those are the most involved ones!

642
00:30:19,273 --> 00:30:22,099
Right?!
Instead of trying to find out the truth!

643
00:30:22,866 --> 00:30:23,866
Exactly!

644
00:30:26,847 --> 00:30:29,048
I apologize, Tso Ke…
oh, Chef K.

645
00:30:29,073 --> 00:30:30,099
Here you go again
with your “Tso K!”

646
00:30:30,379 --> 00:30:31,546
It’s “Chef K” for you!

647
00:30:31,571 --> 00:30:33,258
Chef K! I’m sorry…

648
00:30:33,283 --> 00:30:34,760
- Chef K…
- I’m sorry.

649
00:30:34,900 --> 00:30:37,380
What’s important is
integrity–

650
00:30:37,405 --> 00:30:40,749
do what is right,
with or without anyone to witness it.

651
00:30:41,110 --> 00:30:42,569
- That’s right.
- Wow.

652
00:30:42,593 --> 00:30:43,681
I’m not the important
one here, though.

653
00:30:43,706 --> 00:30:47,549
I’m very happy for you as you
have cleared your name, Tso K.

654
00:30:47,574 --> 00:30:48,631
- Ah, Tso K…
- Tso K?!

655
00:30:48,656 --> 00:30:51,449
- Tso… Tso K! Chef K!
- What do you mean Tso K?!

656
00:30:51,474 --> 00:30:53,294
Stop it! Chef K!

657
00:30:53,503 --> 00:30:57,298
Why does it seem like you’re all
having a hard time calling me “Chef K”?!

658
00:30:58,380 --> 00:30:59,380
Alright,

659
00:30:59,477 --> 00:31:00,477
starting today,

660
00:31:00,714 --> 00:31:02,614
I will change my name.

661
00:31:03,096 --> 00:31:04,511
You will call me something else!

662
00:31:04,536 --> 00:31:05,867
- Huh?
- What? Huh?

663
00:31:05,953 --> 00:31:07,533
What are we going
to call you now?!

664
00:31:08,688 --> 00:31:10,554
Just call me…

665
00:31:11,314 --> 00:31:12,314
“Tso K!”

666
00:31:12,509 --> 00:31:13,556
“Tso K?”

667
00:31:13,959 --> 00:31:14,959
“Tso K?”

668
00:31:14,984 --> 00:31:17,053
It’s tsOK to be “Tso K!”

669
00:31:20,338 --> 00:31:25,443
Tso K! Tso K! Tso K! Tso K!
Tso K! Tso K! Tso K!

670
00:31:25,468 --> 00:31:26,896
Alright, alright, wait up!

671
00:31:26,921 --> 00:31:32,969
This is what you call the National
Uncle of Barangay Singko!

672
00:31:33,447 --> 00:31:34,447
Tso K!

673
00:31:38,883 --> 00:31:46,268
Tso K! Tso K! Tso K! Tso
K! Tso K! Tso K! Tso K!

674
00:31:46,293 --> 00:31:47,581
See, Tso K?

675
00:31:48,220 --> 00:31:53,545
It hits different when you
can brag about your name.

676
00:31:53,823 --> 00:31:54,943
Am I right, Tash, Andres?

677
00:31:55,061 --> 00:31:56,061
You are correct, Dad!

678
00:31:56,086 --> 00:31:58,349
Our last name “Pers”
hits different, too!

679
00:31:58,374 --> 00:31:59,695
- There you go!
- Dad, I agree.

680
00:31:59,921 --> 00:32:02,075
When you say “Pers”

681
00:32:02,434 --> 00:32:03,541
you immediately
think of good people.

682
00:32:04,904 --> 00:32:06,384
Your family clan, yes, maybe!

683
00:32:07,141 --> 00:32:09,334
But your Dad?

684
00:32:09,368 --> 00:32:10,541
Hmmm…

685
00:32:10,566 --> 00:32:11,566
You’re turning on me again!

686
00:32:11,588 --> 00:32:14,829
What do you have against me?
Why does it always come back to me?

687
00:32:15,397 --> 00:32:17,110
Right?
Instead of being like this,

688
00:32:17,134 --> 00:32:20,467
why don’t you just show
the kids your dance.

689
00:32:20,578 --> 00:32:22,138
- What dance?
- Show off your moves!

690
00:32:23,061 --> 00:32:24,534
Oh come on, please!

691
00:32:24,559 --> 00:32:26,801
The ones in your treasure chest!

692
00:32:27,004 --> 00:32:28,904
Bust it out, bust your dance moves out!

693
00:32:30,865 --> 00:32:32,858
No, no, no, no, no, please.
I’m out!

694
00:32:32,883 --> 00:32:34,345
Let’s go, Chef K!

695
00:32:34,370 --> 00:32:35,507
I’m heading out! I don’t want to!

696
00:32:35,532 --> 00:32:37,353
Come on, show it off!

697
00:32:38,280 --> 00:32:39,680
Come on, come on!

698
00:32:39,705 --> 00:32:46,036
You know him, Tso K,
Tso Paeng, and Tso Pando!

699
00:32:46,070 --> 00:32:47,384
Let it rip!

700
00:32:47,530 --> 00:32:48,530
Wooohh!

701
00:32:51,869 --> 00:32:52,869
Wooh!

702
00:32:54,609 --> 00:32:56,967
- Wooh!
- Go Chef! Yeah!

703
00:32:58,440 --> 00:32:59,440
Wooh!

704
00:33:01,152 --> 00:33:02,152
Go!

705
00:33:02,278 --> 00:33:03,905
Okay! Now you’ve seen it!

706
00:33:04,378 --> 00:33:08,216
Don’t forget,
in happiness and struggles,

707
00:33:08,789 --> 00:33:12,511
Pers is the first, Pers is the hero!
